Installation:

- Make the file 'install.sh' executable via 
  chmod, then run as root

- 'install.sh' takes in two arguments, which are the IP addresses of the RDP VMs

- reboot TC to start into load balancer and then RDP right away

- NOTE: run /opt/rdpstarter/client_starter.sh to manually start load balancer

Uninstallation:

- Make the file 'uninstall.sh' executable via 
  chmod, then run as root
